Description.Text: Modern, quality hotel, situated in the heart of London.

Situated in Kensington, close to Kensington High Street and Kensington Church Street, both famous for excellent shopping and restaurants. Within walking distance of High Street Kensington underground station and both Olympia and Earl's Court Exhibition Centres.
The rooms are medium in size, in very good condition and decorated in pale color schemes, offering a light and airy atmosphere. The marble bathrooms are also in very good condition.
The hotel is very modern and well maintained.
The restaurant on the first floor is decorated in a bright colour scheme, furnished with modern pale wooden furniture, mirrored pillars and large windows offering a light and pleasant area.
The lobby is medium sized, very elegant and modern with a marble floor, central fountain and an escalator offering access to the bar and restaurant on the first floor.
